{"tid":1963871,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黨鐵 : 「程程20%車費扣減」損失約16億元 黨鐵及納稅人平均分攤","createTime":"2020-04-08T12:05:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-08T12:09:35.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f274c370328ba2b18349019400a5ae050dae42a4","tid":1963871,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T12:05:24.000Z","msg":"港鐵下半年程程八折 月票每月減100元<br />\n08.04.2020 19:58<br />\n<br />\n行政長官林鄭月娥宣佈，七月起港鐵車費下調20%，為期六個月，一半損失由政府負擔。港鐵指，會推出為期六個月的「程程20%車費扣減」，是現時3.3%扣減的加強版，同時全月通乘客在六個月內購買月票及都會票，一律減一百元。港鐵指，新一輪措施預算收入損失約16億元，實際金額取決於客量，政府會承擔總收入損失的一半，上限8億元，其餘損失由港鐵承擔。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1279608&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1279608%26csid%3D261_341&d=LgTIxyFtuo0acoW68XVTBTQMt3kYY8c646%2Bk6hbI14w%3D&h=de3d2592\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1279608&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"1dc4dc8c91489422a333f80a4582c9f2c123f792","tid":1963871,"uid":157799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T12:07:23.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，好怕大家忘記了，可唔可以入嚟幫手推一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n［5個月］［整合］大家記唔記得今日係咩日子<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1963297\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1963297</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/04/08/150222_9b725230f319dbfd347dc84fa175d02e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F04%2F08%2F150222_9b725230f319dbfd347dc84fa175d02e.png&h=d712b0ff&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0e719994f7f453da3d531a1c280cf2742f78c79f","tid":1963871,"uid":64345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T12:09:35.000Z","msg":"減派息<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.